Alexander DiPersia https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexander_DiPersia 0 Alexander John DiPersia (born March 6, 1982) is an American actor known for his role in the 2016 horror film Lights Out. DiPersia's first role was a minor cameo in the 2007 survival horror film, I Am Legend.
